         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶  ¶ bot Garden ¶ 30 Apr. ¶  ¶ 1858. ¶ My dear Mr Bunce. ¶  ¶ I received this day a letter from Mr Dallachi, ¶ i.e. J. Dallachy.Letter not found. ¶  ¶ who is procuring for this garden seedli...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">58.04.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Daniel Bunce</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS MS SEQUENCE, Australian Box 4/1, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS damaged, with a corner of the sheet missing. All [...] in this transcription correspond to the missing part of the sheet.</p>
               </note>Melbourne<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>bot Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">30 Apr.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1858.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Mr Bunce.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I received this day a letter from Mr Dallachi,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. J. Dallachy.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>who is procuring for this garden seedlings at the Grampians,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which he forwarded by the Royal Mail at Mount Sturgeon. The letter bears no date &amp; the Postmark is illegible. But I presume it arrived about the latter part of this week at Geelong.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Not knowing, whether to apply to the postmaster, the postman or the railway agent at Geelong for the plants, I hope you will show us the favor of ascertaining where the box went to and send it on with a bill of any expenses incurred for the transit, which I shall pay immediately. The box contains probably valuable things, which unless very carefully packed might<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[...]<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>journey [...]</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg to [...] a few seeds [...] Feegee<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Fiji?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Island [...] having pods [...] long &amp; furnish[ing] an excellent vegeta[ble]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">With my best wishes for your welfare I remain,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your humble</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope you recovered your health &amp; will early apply for such plants of ours as you may yet require.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[...] [enclo]se the bags [...] soil duely [...] and I should [...] thankful for [...] filling them.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M was attempting to create a 'magazine' of soil types; see M to J. O'Shanassy, 1 April 1858.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
